00:14:48,829 --> 00:14:52,208
♪Fire devours tears♪

193
00:14:52,637 --> 00:14:56,076
♪Cries fade in the smoke♪

194
00:14:56,573 --> 00:15:00,112
♪Storms gather♪

195
00:15:00,189 --> 00:15:03,875
♪Glory falls like ashes♪

196
00:15:04,317 --> 00:15:07,743
♪Sleeves flutter♪

197
00:15:07,965 --> 00:15:11,511
♪You sing of love and hate
on high stage♪

198
00:15:12,157 --> 00:15:15,607
♪Yearning brings only sorrow♪

199
00:15:15,741 --> 00:15:20,027
♪But in your eyes, I found resolve♪

200
00:15:21,469 --> 00:15:25,407
♪After one final song of parting♪

201
00:15:25,501 --> 00:15:29,266
♪We'll meet again only through tears♪

202
00:15:29,533 --> 00:15:33,086
♪Silently, pain blossoms♪

203
00:15:33,341 --> 00:15:36,938
♪In the flames, we embrace♪

204
00:15:37,117 --> 00:15:41,034
♪After one last song of joy and grief♪

205
00:15:41,437 --> 00:15:44,770
♪Lovers sigh under the endless moon♪.

206
00:15:44,893 --> 00:15:48,537
♪Your face, like a mirage♪

207
00:15:48,701 --> 00:15:55,562
♪Becomes clear again in the ruins♪
